Getting Logical

Notes: We can assign the new column, for this example assign 1 for user that using mobile(at least a like on mobile) With this we can actually create a new question. What are the ratio user using mobile

summary(pf$mobile_likes > 0)
##    Mode   FALSE    TRUE    NA's 
## logical   35056   63947       0
#mobile_check_in <- NA
pf$mobile_check_in <- ifelse(pf$mobile_likes > 0, 1, 0)
pf$mobile_check_in <- factor(pf$mobile_check_in)
sum(pf$mobile_check_in == 1)/length(pf$mobile_check_in)
## [1] 0.6459097
#sum(pf$gender)
#by(pf$mobile_check_in, pf$gender, sum)
sum(pf$mobile_likes)
## [1] 10505832
